                                                        BIRAKILACAK</p>
                                                    <p
                                                        style="color: #134e4a; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0;">
                                                        {{dropoffLocation}}</p>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <!-- Details -->
